    "Specifically, a hybrid framework of artificial intelligence is proposed, which focuses on the way to provide targeted recommendations for the implementation of integrated standard lesson plans, which will be the main tool for creating flexible differentiated pedagogical programs that will perfectly meet the personal needs and particularities of each student.",
